S jpmtwg pf-28_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Hey everyone! Yes, you read that right: the Northern Lights were spotted in Wales! I’m still wrapping my head around it! We were staying up at Hilston Park, high above the clouds, where I thought I’d have the perfect view for spotting anything spectacular in the night sky. And just imagine—right over us that night, the Northern Lights put on a rare, magical show!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-6b48" data-pf-type="Section" id="text_image" class="sc-knuQPt cVHHwo pf-30_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-kRRxPL eBhmAi"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-31_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:5px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-32_"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-33_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-iapVNj iUcVvL pf-34_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Aurora_Borealis_Over_Wales_Jaden_s_Story_of_Wonder_and_Disappointment_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1731064026" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Aurora_Borealis_Over_Wales_Jaden_s_Story_of_Wonder_and_Disappointment_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1731064026 1536w" width="2651" height="1768" alt="Aurora Borealis Over Wales Jaden’s Story of Wonder and Disappointment - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Aurora Borealis Over Wales Jaden’s Story of Wonder and Disappointment - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bVHBsO cFdcpI pf-35_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-36_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by GaudiLab via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Col